{"tid":1826890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴師出動 -- 中西區DO黃何詠詩 — omb、hab、had、csb、icac見！(612 Reminder)","createTime":"2020-01-16T13:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T13:29:29.000Z","uid":266051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c889c40a3d1d681230c338cd4d61e8cd3289f56c","tid":1826890,"uid":266051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"呢舊生物可謂劣跡斑斑，續18年大媽式行為 &mdash;&mdash; 搵附近大廈業委會「扮街坊」撐場支持砍kongu古樹後，今日又再柒多次。一眾區議員係議會動議譴責鄧小強時，居然發老脾話因為唔認同立場就同鄧小強一齊離場。先唔講呢舊生物擅離職守，正苦都成日講作為公墓猿必須政治中立。抵佢無得去局，走黎做DO扮小丑，369呢啲傻鳩AO係唔洗擇日。<br />\n<br />\n有見於此，我地決定開佢file，度埋投訴Template歡迎投訴師全面進場。迫不及待好想玩玩了。<br />\n<br />\nTemplate link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/投訴中西區民政事務專員黃何詠詩涉嫌公職人員行為失當及違反公務員守則-01-16\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2F%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E4%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E9%BB%83%E4%BD%95%E8%A9%A0%E8%A9%A9%E6%B6%89%E5%AB%8C%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6%E5%8F%8A%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87-01-16&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=8ca610de\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegra.ph/投訴中西區民政事務專員黃何詠詩涉嫌公職人員行為失當及違反公務員守則-01-16</a><br />\n<br />\n#反極權運動"},{"pid":"be4ae3a6d6872bb547ccb56ad28d426e19d74a9b","tid":1826890,"uid":10471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b9b640f88b64d2cd38b9d87229395ae7e760e9","tid":1826890,"uid":121173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}